	&lt;li&gt;Professor of the Chair of Urology at the Pavlov First Saint-Petersurg State Medical University, Deputy Chairman of the Saint-Petersburg Scientific Society of Urology named after S.P.Feodorov, member of editorial board of the Journal of Urology, member of the Work Group of the Chief Urologist of the Russian Ministry of Health on development of guidelines and protocols of medical care in the sphere of Urology. &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Member of the Surgery Expert Group, Central Attestation Committee of the Russian Ministry of Health in the North-Western Federal Region of Russia. &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Chief Urologist of the Petrogradsky Region of Saint-Petersburg, Chair of the Committee for work with members of the European Urology Association. &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Author of more than 200 publications in Russian and foreign scientific journals, co-author of the textbook on Urology and the Russian National Guidelines on Urology.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Prof. Korneev had numerous practical training programs in the sphere of Urology and Andrology in the Russian, European and American hospitals and reproduction centres. &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Master of all current methods of diagnosis and treatment of male infertility, erectile dysfunction and other urological disorders. Since 1998, one of the professional areas of Prof. Korneev has been minimally invasive surgeries aimed at sperm retrieval from testicles or epididymides for use in the ART programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;";s:18:"~UF_DESCRIPTION_EN";s:1433:"<ul>
	<li>Professor of the Chair of Urology at the Pavlov First Saint-Petersurg State Medical University, Deputy Chairman of the Saint-Petersburg Scientific Society of Urology named after S.P.Feodorov, member of editorial board of the Journal of Urology, member of the Work Group of the Chief Urologist of the Russian Ministry of Health on development of guidelines and protocols of medical care in the sphere of Urology. </li>
	<li>Member of the Surgery Expert Group, Central Attestation Committee of the Russian Ministry of Health in the North-Western Federal Region of Russia. </li>
	<li>Chief Urologist of the Petrogradsky Region of Saint-Petersburg, Chair of the Committee for work with members of the European Urology Association. </li>
	<li>Author of more than 200 publications in Russian and foreign scientific journals, co-author of the textbook on Urology and the Russian National Guidelines on Urology.</li>
